paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the amyloid fibril disrupting activities of extracts from Juglans plants on TTR amyloidosis, focusing on the V30M TTR variant. No new TTR variants are reported.

challenges: The paper did not report any new TTR variants, only discussed the V30M variant in the context of amyloid fibril disruption assays.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper primarily focuses on the biochemical assays and potential therapeutic compounds for TTR amyloidosis, specifically targeting the V30M variant for testing purposes.
